OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,7,Fenough to give the odd light shower
OL,8,Ffrom time to time. Feeling a little
OL,9,Ffresher.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely dry overnight with a
OL,12,Fmix of cloud and clear spells. Turning
OL,13,Fchilly in any prolonged clear spells,
OL,14,Fespecially in rural areas.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FDry on Wednesday with a mix
OL,17,Fof cloud and sunny spells. Sunshine
OL,18,Ftending to increase throughout the
OL,19,Fafternoon, and with lighter winds it
OL,20,Fbegin to feel warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
